    <title>Water contributor: Nelson Switzer</title>
    <description>Nelson Switzer is vice president and chief sustainability officer of Nestle Waters North America. His goal is to help Nestle Waters embed the principles of sustainable development into business decision-making so they may create natural, social and economic capital that benefits all. Nelson has nearly 20 years of experience as an environmental and social adviser and advocate for global and local, public- and private-sector companies, governments, academia, associations and advocacy groups.
</description>
